	   <tr><td colspan=2>I've killed Coloth a few times. He's level 35 and very tough for his level. He has high magic resist and runs very fast. Don't try to solo him at 35. You'll die or get him to half health before you have to zone and let someone else have an easyish kill. <br><br>As far as I'm aware he has a random spawn point. He used to be seen daily (sometimes even hourly) but he is much rarer these days. You may end up waiting days for him to appear, and you won't be the only one waiting! <br><br>The bow is dropped on average 30-50% of the time, so you have a 1 in 2 to 1 in 3 chance of getting one. <br><br>As far as the lower level guy is concerned I've never seen him so can't comment on him or whether he drops the bow. It seems a very good bow for a lvl 20 drop.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
